Body: Description: Initially saw ERROR 5 (checksum) and later saw ERROR 2 (maximum retries). I need help to further diagnose.
What We've Learned Updated: The customer faced an error when they tried to update the EPP Server during the time when the update was not available for download.

Next Steps Updated: The issue was addressed and the customer can update the server whenever they can.
Waiting for the confirmation if the ticket can be closed.
